    <span class="main_copy_font">Fresh clothes, fresh water! My Fresh Shirt is committed to improving your quality of life by providing a convenient laundry and dry cleaning solution that never sacrifices professional quality and top notch customer service. Why stop there? Because we’re not content with just improving our quality of life.  We want to help others too!</span>
