    </span>
    <br>
    <br>
    <span class="main_copy_font">All donations to MY FRESH WATER will result in the direct funding of the building of wells. We set concrete goals to produce tangible results. Safe drinking water is not an issue we take lightly. Why remain neutral when you can take a proactive stance? Join MY FRESH WATER today!</span>
    <a href="#0">back to top </a>
