    <a name="3" id="3"></a>
    <span class="subtitleGreen">HOW DO YOU CONTRIBUTE? </span>
    <br>
    <br>
    <span class="main_copy_font">To start contributing, simply go to the Eco-Logic tab on your dashboard page. There you can see how much water you have saved thus far. Then you can determine whether or not you would like to donate. We appreciate everyone’s effort in helping to provide safe & clean drinking water to those who need it most.  
        <br>
        <br>
        Want to contribute more? Not currently a member of My Fresh Shirt? Purchase a MY FRESH WATER certificate at our store or after placing an order by adding a “special item” to your service and you can help in providing clean, safe drinking water to those who really need it.  
        <br>
        <br>
        Imagine, the next time you change your clothes, you can be changing the world. 
